# Import combined explicit model file (.pexp) and re-export, checking round-trip
# Note: order differences between sym/explicit engines only affect export-from-prism-source,
# not import-from-explicit-then-re-export, so -ex is safe to include here.

-importmodel robot.prism.pexp -exportmodel robot.prism.pexp
-importmodel robot.prism.pexp -exportmodel robot.prism.pexp -ex
-importmodel robot.prism.exact.pexp -exportmodel robot.prism.exact.pexp -exact
